item.title: Can someone send me the link to get the cache please?
item.dc:creator: @Sepranem Sepranem
item.description:
@Sepranem wrote:

http://www.moparisthebest.com/cache/cache.zip

the reason your cache is being deleted is because the whole cache isn’t being downloaded (this normally happens on dial-up). just close all the programs that use your internet connection then try to manually download the cache from the link above. then when it’s finished, manually extract it to your “C:\WINDOWS.mpr_file_store32” folder, then it should work like a charm
